<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> Competent authorities for exercising supplementary supervision </inglise>
<eesti> T&auml;iendava j&auml;relevalve teostamiseks p&auml;devad asutused </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Supplementary supervision shall be exercised by the competent authorities of the Member State in which the insurance undertaking has received official authorisation under Article 6 of Directive 73/239/EEC or Article 6 of Directive 79/267/EEC. </inglise>
<eesti> T&auml;iendavat j&auml;relevalvet teostavad selle liikmesriigi p&auml;devad asutused, kus kindlustusseltsile on antud ametlik tegevusluba vastavalt direktiivi 73/239/EM&Uuml; artiklile 6 v&otilde;i direktiivi 79/267/EM&Uuml; artiklile 6. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Where insurance undertakings authorised in two or more Member States have as their parent undertaking the same insurance holding company, reinsurance undertaking, non-member-country insurance undertaking or mixed-activity insurance holding company, the competent authorities of the Member States concerned may reach agreement as to which of them will be responsible for exercising supplementary supervision. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui kahes v&otilde;i enamas liikmesriigis tegevusluba omavate kindlustusseltside emaettev&otilde;tja on &uuml;ks ja seesama kindlustusvaldusettev&otilde;tja, edasikindlustusselts, kolmanda riigi kindlustusselts v&otilde;i segakindlustusvaldusettev&otilde;tja, v&otilde;ivad liikmesriikide p&auml;devad asutused kokku leppida, kes neist vastutab t&auml;iendava j&auml;relevalve eest. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Where a Member State has more than one competent authority for the prudential supervision of insurance undertakings and reinsurance undertakings, such Member State shall take the requisite measures to organise coordination between those authorities. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui liikmesriigis on kindlustusseltside ja edasikindlustusseltside usaldatavusnormatiivide t&auml;itmise j&auml;relevalveks rohkem kui &uuml;ks p&auml;dev asutus, v&otilde;tab see liikmesriik k&otilde;neluste asutuste t&ouml;&ouml; koosk&otilde;lastamiseks vajalikud meetmed. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> Availability and quality of information </inglise>
<eesti> Teabe k&auml;ttesaadavus ja kvaliteet </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall prescribe that the competent authorities shall require that every insurance undertaking subject to supplementary supervision shall have adequate internal control mechanisms in place for the production of any data and information relevant for the purposes of such supplementary supervision. </inglise>
