<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall provide that their competent authorities responsible for exercising supplementary supervision shall have access to any information which would be relevant for the purpose of supervision of an insurance undertaking subject to such supplementary supervision. </inglise>
