<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall provide that their competent authorities may carry out within their territory, themselves or through the intermediary of persons whom they appoint for that purpose, on-the-spot verification of the information referred to in paragraph 1 at: </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid n&auml;evad ette, et nende p&auml;devad asutused v&otilde;ivad nende territooriumil ise v&otilde;i selleks ametisse m&auml;&auml;ratud isikute vahendusel kohapeal kontrollida l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud teavet j&auml;rgmistes kohtades: </eesti>
<inglise> - the insurance undertaking subject to supplementary supervision, </inglise>
