<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> In the case referred to in Article 2(1), Member States shall require that an adjusted solvency calculation be carried out in accordance with Annex I. </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 2 l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud juhul n&otilde;uab liikmesriik korrigeeritud maksej&otilde;ulisuse arvutamist vastavalt I lisale. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Any related undertaking, participating undertaking or related undertaking of a participating undertaking shall be included in the calculation referred to in paragraph 1. </inglise>
